snippet.textDisplay:
Listing to your words, 
My mind rests in peace with these faithful wives,  
Even desire itself fades in this still moment.  
I feel full, flowing through every pore of my being,  
Connected to every beautiful now that surrounds me.  
Each moment calls—worthy of lifting my resting eyelids,  
For all the worlds are dancing within me.  
a sufi
